623
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:21,780
What?

624
00:36:21,980 --> 00:36:23,300
You think I can't do it?

625
00:36:23,300 --> 00:36:24,380
A toy boy like you

626
00:36:24,460 --> 00:36:25,660
can only do it in dreams.

627
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:28,540
Then I'll appoint the team lead.

628
00:36:34,140 --> 00:36:35,040
Ma Tian

629
00:36:36,180 --> 00:36:37,540
will be the team lead.

630
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:41,040
He and coach are in charge of training.

631
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:44,500
Why is he the team lead?

632
00:36:45,700 --> 00:36:47,620
Because you're the student in this school.

633
00:36:48,100 --> 00:36:49,640
That means you should obey our arrangement.

634
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:51,700
He has to prove himself qualified for this.

635
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:52,900
Let him run a lap with me.

636
00:36:52,900 --> 00:36:55,080
If he wins, I'll accept that.

637
00:36:55,380 --> 00:36:56,020
What?

638
00:36:56,700 --> 00:36:58,300
You're in charge of school arrangements?

639
00:36:59,980 --> 00:37:01,140
Don't accept that.

640
00:37:01,300 --> 00:37:02,340
You can't win.

641
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:04,660
Okay, Mister.

642
00:37:04,740 --> 00:37:06,220
I think I should prove I'm qualified.

643
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:07,140
I'll run with him.

644
00:37:23,180 --> 00:37:24,980
How can he win?

645
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:26,660
He's over-confident.

646
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:31,260
You decide how we race.

647
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:32,420
Or you'll say I bully you again.

648
00:37:33,740 --> 00:37:34,900
You decide it.

649
00:37:35,020 --> 00:37:36,860
It's you who object it, not me.

650
00:37:38,060 --> 00:37:39,520
Okay. We'll run for 10 laps.

651
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:41,380
One lap is 400 meters only.

652
00:37:41,380 --> 00:37:42,720
The first one finishing it wins.

653
00:37:43,060 --> 00:37:43,860
Okay.

654
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:53,460
Run!

655
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:01,340
Doggo, come on!

656
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:02,660
Ma Tian, come on!

657
00:38:11,740 --> 00:38:13,140
Doggo, come on!

658
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:19,260
Look. What are they doing?

659
00:38:19,260 --> 00:38:20,340
Doggo got objection to appointing him as the team lead,

660
00:38:20,340 --> 00:38:21,260
