661
00:38:21,340 --> 00:38:22,260
You must be kidding.

662
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:23,580
Who can defeat Doggo?

663
00:38:51,540 --> 00:38:52,880
I can't run anymore. I'm tired.

664
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:07,980
What is he saying?

665
00:39:08,380 --> 00:39:09,500
Why did they stop?

666
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:15,100
Why do you stop?

667
00:39:15,180 --> 00:39:16,180
Why do you stop?

668
00:39:16,660 --> 00:39:17,620
I'm tired.

669
00:39:17,660 --> 00:39:18,700
What happened, Doggo?

670
00:39:18,780 --> 00:39:19,420
Are you okay?

671
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:20,740
Yes, let's go.

672
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:29,260
Why are you standing there?

673
00:39:29,260 --> 00:39:30,140
Let's go.

674
00:39:30,180 --> 00:39:30,980
Come with us.

675
00:39:31,180 --> 00:39:33,380
- Come. - Come.

676
00:39:33,540 --> 00:39:34,500
I'll take a break.

677
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:35,100
You won't go?

678
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:36,580
You go first. I'll take a break.

679
00:39:37,660 --> 00:39:38,700
We can wait for him.

680
00:39:40,040 --> 00:39:41,120
Go that way.

681
00:39:42,660 --> 00:39:44,380
Doggo is weird.

682
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:21,520
Tu.

683
00:40:33,660 --> 00:40:35,380
You've worn out another pair of shoes?

684
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:37,360
Haven't I just bought them for you?

685
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,380
I've worn them for a semester.

686
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:40,420
Just bought them?

687
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:42,940
Don't act like

688
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:44,160
I owe you this.

689
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:45,480
Wear them or go barefoot.

690
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:46,380
I...

691
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,540
Move away.

692
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:55,540
Whatever. So stingy you are.

693
00:41:10,940 --> 00:41:11,780
Want some?

694
00:41:13,300 --> 00:41:14,180
What's wrong?

695
00:41:14,180 --> 00:41:15,540
You look unhappy.

696
00:41:16,260 --> 00:41:17,660
I've been here for days.

697
00:41:17,900 --> 00:41:19,180
But I still can't find him.

698
00:41:19,980 --> 00:41:21,700
Okay, we can transfer to another school.

699
00:41:22,300 --> 00:41:22,880
No.

700
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:24,740
Then what should we do?

701
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:27,320
He's good at math.

702
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:29,220
Will he go for Mathematical Olympiad?

703
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:32,300
I'm still here and he's going.

704
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:34,020
Do you think it's possible?

705
