708
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,780
That's long.

709
00:41:43,940 --> 00:41:45,620
He plays basketball well.

710
00:41:45,660 --> 00:41:46,660
There are matches recently.

711
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:48,260
He must've gone for training.

712
00:41:50,940 --> 00:41:51,740
Maybe.

713
00:41:54,660 --> 00:41:55,780
It must be.

714
00:41:56,620 --> 00:41:57,760
I must find him.

715
00:42:01,980 --> 00:42:02,580
Tu Jun,

716
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:04,020
