719
00:42:06,460 --> 00:42:07,740
Why me again?

720
00:42:08,060 --> 00:42:09,340
They are all scared of you.

721
00:42:09,660 --> 00:42:10,300
If it's you,

722
00:42:10,300 --> 00:42:11,300
