728
00:42:21,060 --> 00:42:22,500
Don't talk nonsense.

729
00:42:22,580 --> 00:42:23,220
Zhu Weijiao.

730
00:42:23,260 --> 00:42:23,940
Hurry.

731
00:42:23,980 --> 00:42:25,260
Isn't it a boy and a girl.

732
00:42:25,260 --> 00:42:26,340
I won't go.

733
00:42:26,500 --> 00:42:27,340
I don't want to go with him.

734
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:29,540
They'll check every class?

735
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:30,940
Yes, every class.

736
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:34,020
Miss, I can go.

737
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:35,400
