738
00:42:35,780 --> 00:42:36,360
OK.

739
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:48,900
Doggo is that charming.

740
00:42:50,340 --> 00:42:51,660
You don't know

741
00:42:51,700 --> 00:42:52,460
