742
00:42:52,460 --> 00:42:53,540
We grew up together.

743
00:42:54,460 --> 00:42:55,340
You're right.

744
00:42:57,300 --> 00:42:58,140
Cool.

745
00:42:59,700 --> 00:43:00,380
Okay.

746
00:43:00,380 --> 00:43:02,060
Let's do eye exercise.

747
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:05,340
Eye exercise begins.

748
00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:07,460
Close your eyes.

749
00:43:09,300 --> 00:43:10,800
That's "good".

750
00:43:13,060 --> 00:43:15,240
A girl comes between Doggo and me.

751
00:43:16,380 --> 00:43:17,620
Bad girl.

752
00:43:18,460 --> 00:43:20,220
Don't know what her purpose is.

753
00:43:24,100 --> 00:43:24,820
Why do you laugh?

754
00:43:25,380 --> 00:43:26,500
Something on my face?

755
00:43:26,900 --> 00:43:27,740
No.

756
00:43:28,020 --> 00:43:29,060
Why do you laugh then?

757
00:43:31,300 --> 00:43:33,340
I like you chattering.

758
00:43:33,740 --> 00:43:34,340
Lively.

759
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:38,220
You asked to sit beside me.

760
00:43:38,220 --> 00:43:39,140
Don't report that

761
00:43:39,180 --> 00:43:40,700
I'm a bad influence on you.

762
00:43:41,140 --> 00:43:41,940
Influence me what?

763
00:43:42,820 --> 00:43:43,540
Study?

764
00:43:43,620 --> 00:43:44,240
Yes.

765
00:43:45,620 --> 00:43:47,380
I can be the first one with my eyes closed.

766
00:43:50,580 --> 00:43:51,740
You're so awesome.

767
00:43:56,020 --> 00:43:56,700
By the way,

768
00:43:56,700 --> 00:43:59,580
how many of them do you think I should button up?

769
00:43:59,660 --> 00:44:00,300
All.

770
00:44:03,100 --> 00:44:03,700
And

771
00:44:04,220 --> 00:44:06,500
