772
00:44:06,540 --> 00:44:07,900
Just go through the motions.

773
00:44:07,900 --> 00:44:09,140
No, you're wrong.

774
00:44:09,180 --> 00:44:10,580
We need to check eye exercise

775
00:44:10,580 --> 00:44:12,940
