776
00:44:19,820 --> 00:44:21,940
Why do you come with me to check eye exercise?

777
00:44:21,940 --> 00:44:22,740
What do you think?

778
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:27,420
I'll guess.

779
00:44:30,700 --> 00:44:31,620
Well,

780
00:44:31,980 --> 00:44:33,140
a young girl

781
00:44:33,660 --> 00:44:34,540
can easily

782
00:44:34,660 --> 00:44:35,540
fall for someone.

783
00:44:36,020 --> 00:44:37,940
I do admire your imagination.

784
00:44:39,220 --> 00:44:41,300
Doggo, who's this girl?

785
00:44:42,020 --> 00:44:43,060
Okay.

786
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,660
Stop yelling.

787
00:44:44,900 --> 00:44:46,100
Don't think I'll show mercy,

788
00:44:46,140 --> 00:44:47,420
