789
00:44:48,420 --> 00:44:49,400
Especially you.

790
00:44:52,140 --> 00:44:53,700
The students of this class are all here?

791
00:45:17,700 --> 00:45:18,660
Do you play basketball?

792
00:45:20,580 --> 00:45:21,180
Yes.

793
00:45:21,660 --> 00:45:23,180
I'm good at it.

794
00:45:23,180 --> 00:45:24,500
I'm a great player.

795
00:45:24,620 --> 00:45:26,100
Who's the best player in our school?

796
00:45:26,100 --> 00:45:27,060
My big brother.

797
00:45:27,100 --> 00:45:27,700
Back then,

798
00:45:27,780 --> 00:45:28,940
