799
00:45:28,940 --> 00:45:29,900
Who's your big brother?

800
00:45:29,940 --> 00:45:30,620
Liu Wenqin.

801
00:45:31,340 --> 00:45:32,740
The last class. Let's go.

802
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:54,740
Are there any students on the sick leave?

803
00:45:54,980 --> 00:45:55,780
No.

804
00:46:15,900 --> 00:46:17,300
Don't be depressed.

805
00:46:17,540 --> 00:46:19,340
I know what you're thinking.

806
00:46:20,060 --> 00:46:21,220
What do you know?

807
00:46:23,060 --> 00:46:24,340
You like being alone with me.

808
00:46:24,420 --> 00:46:25,700
I know that.

809
00:46:25,740 --> 00:46:26,380
Tomorrow,

810
00:46:26,460 --> 00:46:28,660
we'll check together again.

811
00:46:29,220 --> 00:46:30,100
Ridiculous.

812
00:46:30,140 --> 00:46:31,060
Who wants to be alone with you?

813
00:46:31,100 --> 00:46:32,840
Who wants to check with you?

814
00:46:41,700 --> 00:46:44,460
Using two extreme ways

815
00:46:44,780 --> 00:46:46,140
