819
00:46:55,900 --> 00:46:58,959
You think she likes you?

820
00:47:00,020 --> 00:47:01,039
Of course.

821
00:47:01,380 --> 00:47:02,380
I knew that.

822
00:47:03,300 --> 00:47:04,220
She's just arrived here,

823
00:47:04,220 --> 00:47:05,140
