824
00:47:09,960 --> 00:47:12,380
We're in the last year before we notice it.

825
00:47:13,540 --> 00:47:14,380
Yes.

826
00:47:15,380 --> 00:47:16,580
It's great to be with you guys.

827
00:47:17,180 --> 00:47:18,100
Why?

828
00:47:19,140 --> 00:47:20,580
Our grades are so poor.

829
00:47:21,780 --> 00:47:23,020
Do you know what that mean?

830
00:47:23,420 --> 00:47:25,180
It means we'll be very poor.

831
00:47:26,500 --> 00:47:27,740
Though what you said is right,

832
00:47:27,740 --> 00:47:28,980
I wanted to say

833
00:47:29,180 --> 00:47:31,060
