842
00:48:04,180 --> 00:48:05,180
I didn't!

843
00:48:11,140 --> 00:48:12,100
Useless.

844
00:48:12,140 --> 00:48:14,060
Bullied by a little girl.

845
00:48:18,180 --> 00:48:18,900
What are you looking at!

846
00:48:20,900 --> 00:48:22,260
None of your business!

847
00:48:25,860 --> 00:48:27,060
That girl is so fierce.

848
00:48:27,060 --> 00:48:27,940
Why are you running?

849
00:48:28,180 --> 00:48:29,580
She kicked the shoot out of me.

850
00:48:30,719 --> 00:48:31,340
Stop there!

851
00:48:31,380 --> 00:48:32,500
Stop there!

852
00:48:35,460 --> 00:48:36,100
Stop there!

853
00:48:37,060 --> 00:48:37,660
Why are you running?

854
00:48:37,660 --> 00:48:39,100
Don't run if you have guts.

855
00:48:39,220 --> 00:48:40,260
- Stop there! - Don't run!

856
00:48:40,300 --> 00:48:40,900
Stop there!

857
00:48:40,980 --> 00:48:41,620
Stop there!

858
00:49:05,140 --> 00:49:06,700
Brother, it's them.

859
00:49:07,380 --> 00:49:08,900
This is my big brother, Liu Wenqin.

860
00:49:21,380 --> 00:49:22,639
You think you're something?

861
00:49:26,020 --> 00:49:26,700
You too.

862
00:49:37,260 --> 00:49:39,180
I spent a year finishing it.

863
00:49:39,980 --> 00:49:41,340
You said I'd be stronger.

864
00:49:43,140 --> 00:49:44,420
It's been a year.

865
00:49:44,580 --> 00:49:45,860
You still haven't got stronger.

866
00:49:48,180 --> 00:49:48,820
It's been a while.

867
00:49:48,820 --> 00:49:49,500
Yes.

868
00:49:51,300 --> 00:49:52,180
This is Doggo.

869
00:49:52,180 --> 00:49:53,220
Doggo.

870
00:49:56,500 --> 00:49:57,100
You can go.

871
00:49:57,660 --> 00:49:59,620
Qin, we really miss you.

872
00:49:59,660 --> 00:50:01,220
I miss you too, Qin.

873
00:50:01,420 --> 00:50:02,140
Bullshit.

874
00:50:04,460 --> 00:50:05,500
Have some food. My treat.

875
00:50:06,140 --> 00:50:06,860
What will we eat?

876
00:50:07,940 --> 00:50:08,860
Grill?

877
00:50:10,780 --> 00:50:11,780
