878
00:50:14,060 --> 00:50:15,580
Qin is doing this business.

879
00:50:16,620 --> 00:50:17,660
He was such a man.

880
00:50:17,820 --> 00:50:18,980
How could it be?

881
00:50:19,020 --> 00:50:20,420
He's grilling.

882
00:50:31,340 --> 00:50:32,300
What are you looking at?

883
00:50:35,500 --> 00:50:36,940
I have to live.

884
00:50:41,420 --> 00:50:42,100
Have some.

885
00:50:58,100 --> 00:50:59,220
He must have been through a lot

886
00:50:59,780 --> 00:51:01,300
in this year.

887
00:51:10,860 --> 00:51:12,060
Coach is busy today.

888
00:51:12,340 --> 00:51:13,980
I'll train you today.

889
00:51:22,860 --> 00:51:23,460
Team lead Ma,

890
00:51:24,220 --> 00:51:26,660
how will you avenge today?

891
00:51:27,460 --> 00:51:28,780
How about running stairs?

892
00:51:29,060 --> 00:51:30,140
Just 40 rounds will do.

893
00:51:30,340 --> 00:51:31,320
40...

894
00:51:33,900 --> 00:51:35,300
What? You can't?

895
00:51:35,820 --> 00:51:36,500
That's fine.

896
00:51:48,500 --> 00:51:49,140
You don't need to.

897
00:51:49,580 --> 00:51:51,180
Just run to the classroom.

898
00:51:52,740 --> 00:51:53,420
Thank you, team lead.

899
00:51:53,820 --> 00:51:55,100
Is there an end?

900
00:51:55,780 --> 00:51:56,660
I'm not scared.

901
00:51:56,740 --> 00:51:57,940
I'll see whether he

902
00:51:58,020 --> 00:51:58,740
or we will be tired.

903
00:51:58,940 --> 00:52:00,140
It must be us.

904
00:52:00,340 --> 00:52:01,980
We do leapfrog and stair running every day.

905
00:52:02,399 --> 00:52:03,500
I'm exhausted.

906
00:52:03,620 --> 00:52:04,420
I'm not!

907
00:52:05,460 --> 00:52:06,820
I don't want to run.

908
00:52:07,180 --> 00:52:07,800
Big Mouth,

909
00:52:08,180 --> 00:52:09,460
you can get good grades.

910
00:52:09,820 --> 00:52:11,180
You don't need to go to the 16th exam room.

911
00:52:11,540 --> 00:52:14,220
Why do you accompany us to marathon?

912
00:52:15,500 --> 00:52:16,780
Friends support each other for a lifetime.

913
00:52:16,780 --> 00:52:18,180
The one who succeeds first is a rat.

914
00:52:18,580 --> 00:52:19,860
I'll be in the bottom with you.

915
00:52:19,860 --> 00:52:20,920
Stop talking.

916
00:53:12,540 --> 00:53:14,820
I told you! She likes me!

917
00:53:14,980 --> 00:53:15,860
I also said,

918
00:53:15,860 --> 00:53:17,140
I could tell!

919
00:53:17,300 --> 00:53:19,140
That must be the honey-trap of Ma.

920
00:53:23,460 --> 00:53:24,900
I heard that the basketball team restarts training.

921
00:53:24,900 --> 00:53:25,620
Really?

922
00:53:25,620 --> 00:53:26,220
Yes.

923
00:53:26,340 --> 00:53:27,500
They're training now.

924
00:53:27,500 --> 00:53:28,340
Let's see.

925
00:53:28,340 --> 00:53:29,140
Let's go.

926
00:54:32,580 --> 00:54:34,580
Our school hasn't won for a long time.

927
00:54:35,220 --> 00:54:36,060
Yes.

928
00:54:36,100 --> 00:54:37,180
We haven't won,

929
00:54:37,180 --> 00:54:38,260
since Liu Wenqin left.

930
00:54:44,100 --> 00:54:45,580
Why do you remove this poster?

931
00:54:45,660 --> 00:54:46,860
It's the last year's poster.

932
00:54:47,180 --> 00:54:47,940
Where's Liu Wenqin?

933
00:54:48,380 --> 00:54:49,500
He dropped out of school.

934
00:54:49,620 --> 00:54:50,580
Why did he do that?

935
00:54:50,660 --> 00:54:51,500
We have no idea.
